<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Differential flame graphs</b></p><p>You can compare the performance of algorithms, approaches, and even JDKs by comparing two profiler snapshots. In the right-hand part of the toolbar, click <span class="control">Compare With Baseline</span>, then select the other snapshot. The result of the comparison is available in several views, which show you exactly where the difference lies.</p><p class="image"><img src="images/ij-tips-snapshot-diff.png" alt="Differential flame graph showing the comparison of two snapshots" style="border: 1px solid #55555;" /></p></body></html>